photo.alt: Profile of a man in blue trousers and a grey T-shirt with black hair and beard. Feeding small fish to penguins. The 4 penguins are lined up with their wings outstretched in anticipation. The penguin at the front of the line is reaching up to the man for the fish. A metal bucket of fish sits atop a bright orange penguin nest box.

Man in blue shirt and a grey T-shirt with black hair and beard. Feeding leaves from a branch to a tapir. The tapir is reaching up with its flexible nose to reach the leaves on the branch the man is holding.

Man in blue trousers and a grey T-shirt with a blue over shirt with black hair and beard. The man is kissing a Dik-dik. A very small deer. The Dik-dik is standing on hind legs and is stretching to kiss the man. The Dik-dik is grey towards the rump becoming tan towards the front. It has very fragile looking front legs reaching to the manâ€™s chest. It has a spiky hair-do and exceptionally cute, tiny, spiky antlers.

Man in blue trousers, a grey T-shirt  and blue over shirt with black hair and beard. A black lemur sits awkwardly on the manâ€™s left shoulder. It is facing the ground. The man is looking towards the lemur. The manâ€™s left hand is outstretched in front of him handing a small piece of sweet potato in a flat hand covered in a blue latex glove. A pair of grey lemurs are sitting on a rope swing and one lemur has grabbed the sweet potato. The second lemur is behind the first, holding the manâ€™s hand while staring at the sweet potato the other lemur is holding.
